		<text path="audio/module9/m09s04" id="0" ><![CDATA[Companies whose information is unfairly targeted can file suit—and the law is often on their side. Click on each heading to see what can happen when things go wrong.]]></text>		
	</transcript>
	<contentText >
		<text style="width: 490px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><![CDATA[Many companies and people have faced serious consequences for the way they collected information about competing companies or products, as these examples illustrate.]]></text>	
	</contentText>
